        <mxCell id="card_cheap" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;spacingRight=6;fontSize=13;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#FFFFFF);arcSize=6;shadow=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;CHEAP&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• triage_numeric — HGB classifier&lt;br&gt;• retrieve_dense — BiEncoder&lt;br&gt;• compose_l2 — RRF + rerank&lt;br&gt;• compose_triage — logistic stack&lt;br&gt;• compose_novelty — disjunction&lt;br&gt;• rerank_with_evidence — tool overlap" vertex="1">
