        <mxCell id="reg_footer" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=13;fontStyle=2;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#FFFFFF);labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;b&gt;Adaptive execution.&lt;/b&gt;  The controller selects one branch; within active_fault, the four expensive retrievers and verify_with_llm fire only when the cheap path is unconfident (&lt;i&gt;escalation gate&lt;/i&gt;), and the ReAct evidence tools + rerank_with_evidence fire only on low retrieval consensus (&lt;i&gt;reformulation gate&lt;/i&gt;).  Decision precedence: rerank ⟶ compose_l2 ⟶ retrieve_dense.  Every skill output is cached (SkillCache); every invocation is recorded (Trace); the Budget can abort the plan." vertex="1">
